*ipsec-tools-0.7.3-r1 (30 Aug 2011)

  30 Aug 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +ipsec-tools-0.7.3-r1.ebuild, -ipsec-tools-0.6.7-r6.ebuild,
  +files/ipsec-tools-duplicate-header.patch,
  -files/psk.txt.clip, -files/ipsec.conf.sample,
  -files/racoon.sh, -files/dpd-ipsec-tools-client-0.6.5.diff,
  -files/racoon.conf.d.clip:
  Bump to latest, remove all (very legacy) support for using racoon 
  as ike daemon on CLIP.

*ipsec-tools-0.6.7-r6 (11 Jun 2009)

