*ipsec-tools-0.6.7 (07 Dec 2007)

  07 Dec 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +ipsec-tools-0.6.7.ebuild, -ipsec-tools-0.6.5-r5.ebuild:
  Bump to latest stable from Gentoo. Fixes GLSA 200705-09. CLIP 
  changeset is left unchanged from 0.6.5-r5.
  Note however that NAT-T support is now optionnal, and not activated
  at this point in CLIP.

  07 Nov 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  Remove stale ebuilds before 0.6.5-r5.

