  Install a copy of psk.txt in the admin view with the good permission.
  Install psk.txt in the admin view to be able to overwrite it 
  at boot time.
  Add the treatment of this copy in the racoon file.

  10 Aug 2007; EADS D&S <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +ipsec-tools-0.6.5-r3.ebuild, +files/dpd-ipsec-tools-client-0.6.5.diff
